File Name: readme

---------------------------------------------------
HOW TO ADD A PACKAGE TO BE INSTALLED UNDER CHROOT ?
---------------------------------------------------
To add package that needs to be installed under the chroot,
please modify the file "get_pkg.sh" where you can add a
line at the end of the file. The added line should
be "apt-get install <package-name>". 


----------------------------------------------
HOW TO ADD COMMANDS TO SETUP SYSTEM RESOURCE ?
----------------------------------------------
TO add commands, please modify the file "conf_limit.sh"
where you can add lines at the end of the file.


--------------------------------------------------
HOW TO ADD SHELLSCRIPTS FOR RUNNING UNDER CHROOT ?
--------------------------------------------------
To add additional shellscripts, please  modify the file
"setup_ae.sh" where you can add lines at the end of the
file.


---------------------------------------------------------
HOW TO CREATE CHROOT ENVIRONMENT AND RUN ALL_EYES THERE ?
---------------------------------------------------------
Please do the following steps

1. Go to directory "<your-workspace>/all-eyes/src/ae"
2. Issue command "make clobber"
3. Issue command "make"
4. Go to "<your-workspace>/all-eyes/src/ae/bin"
5. Issue command "install_chroot.sh"


